Royal Bites Restaurant Website (Taste Haven) - Project Notes
Project Overview

Taste Haven ek responsive single-page restaurant website hai jo customers ko restaurant ke baare me information, menu, gallery, reviews aur table reservation ki suvidha deti hai.

Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Bootstrap 5
Font Awesome
Responsive Design (Media Queries)
Color Palette
Color	Usage
#000000	Footer Background
#111111	Navbar & Dark Sections
#222222	Cards Background
#FFFFFF	Main Text
#CCCCCC	Secondary Text
#FF6B00	Buttons & Hover Effects
#333333	Borders
